<i>adjective</i>: 흉포하다 [흉포하다], 사납다 [사ː납따], 맵다 [맵따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흉포하다 [흉포하다]</dt><br>
<dd>ferocious; atrocious; brutal</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 매우 흉악하고 포악하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's personality being brutal and violent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사납다 [사ː납따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. violent; fierce</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 행동이 거칠다.</dd><br>
<dd>A personality or behavior being wild.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fierce; ferocious</dd><br>
<dd>생김새가 무섭고 험악하다.</dd><br>
<dd>An appearance being scary and menacing.</dd><br>
<dd>3. violent; fierce</dd><br>
<dd>눈, 비, 바람 등이 몹시 세차다.</dd><br>
<dd>Snow, rain, wind, etc., being very severe.</dd><br>
<dd>4. unlucky; harsh</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 사정이 나쁘다.</dd><br>
<dd>The situation or circumstances being bad.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>맵다 [맵따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spicy; hot</dd><br>
<dd>고추나 겨자처럼 맛이 화끈하고 혀끝을 쏘는 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a tangy taste like red peppers or mustard, which causes a sharp sensation at the tip of the tongue.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ferocious</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 사납고 독하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A person's personality being fierce and violent.</dd><br>
<dd>3. ice-cold; freezing</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 매우 춥다.</dd><br>
<dd>The weather being very cold.</dd><br>
<dd>4. stinging</dd><br>
<dd>연기 등이 눈이나 코를 자극하여 시큰하고 따갑다.</dd><br>
<dd>A person's eyes or nose stinging or burning due to smoke, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>